--de_coldstorm_a4--

Coldstorm is a bomb/defuse map created by J4CK8 and Mikeypilk. It's _a4 but it's actualy closer to _rc1, but there are a couple of bugs and thigns to add.

Included is:
A custom nav (Mostly works-ish)
A custom radar
Custom textures
Some special music
3d skybox

Thanks to TopHATTwaffle for most of the custom textures in the map.

Visit http://jammyleveldesign.blogspot.com to see more of our levels and development info.
